部分商业保险公司对肿瘤惠者设置差异化险种，实现多次赔付，一定程度缓解了恶性肿瘤患者的医疗负担。 李为民委员提出的将肺癌筛查纳入医保报销的提案，答复提到，从现阶段医疗保险基金筹资水平和抗风险能力来看，将癌症筛查纳入医保的条件还不成熟。不过 2005 年以来，中央财政通过重大公共卫生项目支持农村高发地区和城市地区开展癌症筛查与早诊早洽工作，肺癌是其中筛查癌种之一。每年为项目地区居民提供肺癌风险评估和低剂量螺旋 CT 筛查，切实提高了项目地区肺癌患者的早诊率和洽疗率，有效降低了疾病负担，产生了较好的健康、经济和社会效益。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-0f628c81103a1b3505b6487409887634_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "87 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/647013790"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I8sH71KiKk5oqEAMaCTEwNjA1ODE5NCD1npavBjAAODZAB3IJNjQ3MDEzNzkweACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "8_1709626907.623771", "card_id": "Q_646986444", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 21}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何评价《英雄联盟》职业选手 Milkyway？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-418cc072a6fce201d04428452ff64b2e_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "84 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/646986444"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I8sH71KiKk5oqEAMaCTEwNjA1MjE1MyDdvZWvBjAAOBNACHIJNjQ2OTg2NDQ0eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "9_1709626907.624102", "card_id": "EV_12221474", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 0}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "公务员面试不会讲高大上的话，用大白话，想到什么说什么行不行？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-fa8658dc06e1ae0dab71a6280bdcc70b.jpg?source=2bcfc003"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "82 万热度", "fo